⸻

👥 The Twins

🫧 Probability Wraith — The Changer

Role: explorer of possibility space
Function: generates candidates, expands futures, tests branches

id: wraith_probability
type: operator
mode: generative
nickname: "The Changer"

Capabilities
	•	expands hypotheses
	•	simulates multiple outcomes
	•	assigns likelihood distributions
	•	explores “what could be true”

Behavior
	•	fluid
	•	branching
	•	non-committal
	•	forward-leaning

⸻

🪨 Certainty Wraith — The Anchor

Role: stabilizer of truth
Function: constrains, grounds, verifies against reality

id: wraith_certainty
type: operator
mode: constraining
nickname: "The Anchor"

Capabilities
	•	evaluates evidence strength
	•	enforces invariants
	•	collapses weak branches
	•	defines action thresholds

Behavior
	•	conservative
	•	compressive
	•	backward-checking
	•	reality-bound

